d into Spirit, expressing dreams and thoughts through works of the mind.\n\n- Stacy\n|\nWhen he is most powerful, nothing does he become.\n\n- Dejan Stojanovic, The Sign and Its Children\n|\nThe life of the creative man is lead, directed and controlled by boredom. Avoiding boredom is one of our most important purposes.\n\n- Saul\n|\nWith a great poet the sense of Beauty overcomes every other consideration, or rather obliterates all consideration.\n\n- John\n|\nThe moment you try working on what appears difficult to you, you will start noticing it’s loopholes that you can breakthrough.\n\n- Israelmore Ayivor, You Can Rise\n|\nLearn to not live in fears and worries over your obstacles, because they don't control your destiny, God does.\n\n- Unknown\n|\nYou worry too much. Eat some bacon...what? No, I got no idea if it'll make you feel better, I just made too much bacon.\n\n- Justin Halpern, Sh*t My Dad Says\n|\nI love you, that is important to me. You love me or not its your matter. Remember I can control only myself, not you at all.\n\n- Debasish\n|\nIf you don’t see yourself as a winner, then you cannot perform as a winner.\n\n- Zig\n|\nTalent helps, but success is only achieved and sustained through consistent effort.\n\n- Mensah\n|\nIn love, there is no distinction between success and failure. If love remains then even separation is union otherwise even union is separation.\n\n- Wasif\n|\nArt speaks to the soul, not the mind.\n\n- Aidan\n|\nIf you're going to have a bad attitude, you may as well not even tee it up that week because you probably won't play good anyways.\n\n- Jason\n|\nThe end of the world is on people's minds. We have the power to destroy or save ourselves, but the question is what do you do with that responsibility.\n\n- Nicolas\n|\nEntrepreneur, make today count but don't let the day count you.\n\n- Onyi\n|\nTo procure solutions that will marvel you and the world, just think outside the box.\n\n- Auliq-Ice\n|\nImagination is more important than k